@startuml
title Manager Task State Machine

skinparam shadowing false

[*] --> AwakeCycle

state AwakeCycle {
  [*] --> CollectInputs

  CollectInputs --> UpdateDisplay : new sensor data / wakeup
  UpdateDisplay --> CheckLogTimer

  CheckLogTimer --> AppendToBuffer : log interval elapsed
  CheckLogTimer --> SleepPrepare : log interval not elapsed

  AppendToBuffer --> CheckBufferFull
  CheckBufferFull --> QueueFlashWrite : buffer full
  CheckBufferFull --> SleepPrepare : buffer not full

  QueueFlashWrite --> SleepPrepare
}

AwakeCycle --> LoggingStopped : partition full
LoggingStopped --> UpdateDisplayError : show on OLED
UpdateDisplayError --> NotifyUart : print warning
NotifyUart --> SleepPrepare

SleepPrepare --> LightSleep : no pending critical work
LightSleep --> AwakeCycle : wake after 1 second

@enduml
